      "stimulus_html": "",
      "stem_html": "Reaction of <i>cis</i>-2-butene with <i>m</i>-chloroperoxybenzoic acid yields an epoxide different from that obtained by reaction of the trans isomer. Explain.",
      "answers": [],
      "hints": [],
